Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为什么都会聚集到这儿来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了热热闹闹地吃吃东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是在哪儿都能做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.87,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(250,320)\fad(300,300)}然后、朝着下一个景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉那儿的空气都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我今天也是来享受的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就买了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点东西  就麻烦枫同学做饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的笨拙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番茄酱烩饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蔬菜先煮熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后加入法式清汤和番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把饭放进去后搅拌3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尝一下味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:00:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去买什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便选的材料也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是随便选的么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是基本素材都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真不错  在大太阳下做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你买的原来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  接着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵姐看上去很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她原来更加拘谨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点变化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们闹过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个菜单是从哪儿学的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从料理书上看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有实质内容的对话持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这并不让人感到乏味无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而让人觉得十分舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始理解为什么人们会聚集到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是为了确认对方是否幸福才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空真宽广啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里也看不到银河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好歹也算是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是在山上的话就能看到哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  小葵你也能去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己觉得做不到的事才会做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多数的情况下只要努力就能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有仰望过星空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一旦有兴趣了  感觉就能开始看清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又能和其它事物产生联系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河吗  真想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  去看银河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
